    "concept_sort_game": "gikora igitekerezo shira mu rutonde umukino interface kuri categorization kora imyitozo. Kwega ikintu into correct icigwa buckets ku demonstrate understanding ca classification ibitekerezo. Immediate feedback irerekana correct na incorrect placements. imfashanyo 2-4 ibyigwa na any umubare ca sortable ikintu. Gikomeye kuri amajambo tiers, science classifications, canke grammar sorting.",
