      "fakes_heading": "⚠ Fake buttons",
      "fakes_help": "Elements zifite cursor:pointer zisa nko zikandiwe ariko zitagerwaho na keyboard. Impamvu isanzwe: div ifise onClick aho kuba <button> nyabyo. Gukosora: hindura ku <button>, CYANGWA ongeraho tabindex=\"0\" + role=\"button\" + keyboard event handlers.",
      "pos_heading": "⚠ Positive tabindex",
