      "no_label_heading": "🔴 Amazina ya accessibility abura",
      "no_label_help": "Focusable elements zitagira inyandiko, aria-label, aria-labelledby, canke title. Bakoresha screen reader bumva gusa izina rya tag, urugero: \"button\" itagira context. Gukosora: ongeraho aria-label canke inyandiko igaragara.",
      "tip": "Inama: tembera ku rupapuro rw'inyuma rwa lab ukoresha gusa Tab, Shift+Tab, Enter, na Esc. Kanda izina ry'element iyo ari yo yose mu rutonde hejuru ku kuyifocus (urupapuro ruzunguruka niba bikenewe)."
