      "idle": "Kanda \"Kora audit\" ku scan igaragara rya none ku WCAG 2.1 A na AA violations. Iya mbere ifata amasegonda ~2 yo gupakira axe-core (~350 KB minified) kuva muri CDN; izindi zikora ako kanya.",
