      "tip": "Inama: ibibazo vya critical na serious bifunguye busanzwe. Kanda \"Nyereka\" kuri rule iyo ari yo yose ku gufocus no kwerekana element ya mbere igizweho ingaruka. axe-core ikora ~30-50% by'ibibazo nyabyo; vanga na keyboard tour, screen-reader preview, no gusuzuma mu ntoki.",
