        "color_contrast_enhanced": "Inyandiko zimwe ntizihuza n'AAA contrast standard yo hejuru. Abanyeshure ba AA bashobora kuracyazisoma; AAA ni intumbero ikomeye cyane.",
        "image_alt": "Amashusho amwe nta alt text afise. Abanyeshure bakoresha screen readers (impumyi canke bafite low-vision) ntibazumva kintu canke bazumva gusa filename iyo iyi shusho igaragaye.",
